`8Keywords``   : Drink
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * drink <object>

 When you are thirsty, drink something, where "something" could be a fountain
or a container of liquid.  The latter can be bought at 2 south, 1 west, 1 north
of Sendar's Temple of Ul (also known as 'recall').

